<ques id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2006-12-22.2.q0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80273" speakername="Tommy Sheridan (Glasgow) (Sol)" spid="S2W-30255" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-06/wa1222.htm#1" holdingdate="2006-12-15">

  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive what the staffing establishment and structure will be of the fingerprint departments in the Scottish Police Services Authority from 1 April 2007.</p>

